media:group.media:title: Lars Andersen Christmas Archery
media:group.media:description:
Triple trick shooting
Long before I started with trick archery was the impressive American archer Byron Ferguson .
He has hit very small target
Has hit target blindfolded
And hit target with his feet

Just for fun I would try it all at once
A small bell 13 mm
Blindfolded
Bow held with feet

I thought it was almost impossible
but surprisingly it only took 5 minutes to film.

A very lucky shot.
It could be filmed better and in good slow motion.
But I got the idea and immediately put up a camera
just to see if it was possible.
Made a few try throws
and then I hit (it was seen by others)
So I do not want to make a better version!

The bow used in this video Grózer 49 # 28 "

Music:
"Christmas rap" Kevin MacLeod

Merry Christmas and Happy New Year
Lars Andersen
